skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily fortune
des:
Alexa will provide a daily fortune prepared especially for you! Behind the scenes, complex algorithms are used to prepare an appropriate and meaningful fortune for each user of this skill. This means your daily fortune will be different than other users of the skill. 

A new personalized daily fortune is prepared each day! Launch the skill every day to hear your new daily fortune!

To use, simply say, "Alexa, open Daily Fortune!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
